		<item>
		<title>Высокотехнологичная разница между поршневым насосом и роторным насосом для заполнения</title>
		<link>https://www.npackpm.com/ru/%d1%80%d0%b0%d0%b7%d0%bd%d0%b8%d1%86%d0%b0-%d0%bc%d0%b5%d0%b6%d0%b4%d1%83-%d0%bf%d0%be%d1%80%d1%88%d0%bd%d0%b5%d0%b2%d1%8b%d0%bc-%d0%bd%d0%b0%d1%81%d0%be%d1%81%d0%be%d0%bc-%d0%b8-%d1%80%d0%be%d1%82</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Shanghai npack Automation Equipment Co.,ltd]]></dc:creator>
		<pubdate>Tue, 06 Jun 2023 09:23:00 +0000</pubdate>
				<category><![CDATA[Industry News]]></category>
